{
  "stem": "27747.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And back again in Hoszcza when I was freed, the remaining large synagogue, the [POLISH], it was still there, yes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had three synagogues.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was the very big one that my family belonged, one was for the-- small one for the working people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And another one was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We met-- we were met by cousins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, it was not that easy to get to America because every time we would show up to the American consulate, he would want to know where the town Hoszcza is on the map, and we couldn't find it, so we told him it's near Rowne, 30 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What government was it under?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was it Polish, Russian?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was all because of a quarter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If it was the Russian quarter, it was all-- it was all used up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Polish quarter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I patiently explained that it was 1920, it was Poland until '39, it was until '20, and before that, it was the Russian government-- the czarist Russia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said-- well, he wasn't sure which quarter I belonged to, so it was difficult to get to America.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we kept on getting papers from the cousins very patiently all the time, changing-- changing names, changing family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was an addition.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a daughter, Linda.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he-- but we got the papers, the new ones.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And finally, no quarter helped, but the International Refugee Organization was established and took us-- you know, even the boats, the passage was free.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Passage was free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we arrived [INAUDIBLE] to America.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were met with, you know, just cousins that we never met, but I used to write to them in English.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
